WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.933 --> 00:00:07.366
Xiaoya still remembers the first time I saw you

2
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:10.633
You're wearing a little pink dress

3
00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:12.566
Very beautiful.

4
00:00:13.466 --> 00:00:16.366
And playful like an elf

5
00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:19.733
I was immediately attracted to you

6
00:00:19.733 --> 00:00:21.800
I can't help but want to be close to you

7
00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:26.033
But then we hurt each other because of a misunderstanding.

8
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:30.366
I just came up with such a stupid way

9
00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:31.866
Keep you by my side

10
00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:33.200
Xiaoya

11
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:35.766
About your mother

12
00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:37.500
It's all my fault

13
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:41.366
Sorry.

14
00:00:41.566 --> 00:00:44.400
I will definitely compensate you in the future.

15
00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:45.900
Go don't say anymore

16
00:00:46.300 --> 00:00:48.500
Xiaoya, listen to me

17
00:00:49.366 --> 00:00:50.400
Shanshan

18
00:00:51.100 --> 00:00:52.900
I don't care if you did it or not

19
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
I won't pursue it anymore from today

20
00:00:56.333 --> 00:00:59.000
Can we have a good life in the future?

21
00:01:00.933 --> 00:01:02.266
It's too late.

22
00:01:03.300 --> 00:01:04.800
What do you mean it's too late?

23
00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:12.200
I put something on my lip.

24
00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:19.300
Xiao Yang, I love you so much

25
00:01:19.300 --> 00:01:21.033
Why would you do that?

26
00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:23.300
It's You

27
00:01:24.100 --> 00:01:26.033
You killed my mother

28
00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.666
I want you to be buried with him

29
00:01:29.066 --> 00:01:30.066
Ah!

30
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.766
It's all over now.

